​Hello Jacquelin,
I called the general office and was given your contact information as you were the adjuster on this file

I have question regarding this claim and some information for you 
The Insured is requesting a GAP claim We requested a Police report 
The report I received is attached. 
The vehicle was recovered in Damoth Nova Scotia by Canadian Boarder Services 
They indicated that the keys and the ownership were in the vehicle

I have attached the Police report

I am sure you will want the information for your files 
Any information you could provide to me would be helpful.   
Kindest Regards, 
Sean Terkildsen
